a lot less than you think,

566
00:35:18,549 --> 00:35:19,538
plus a finder's fee.

567
00:35:19,650 --> 00:35:20,878
Two percent.

568
00:35:20,985 --> 00:35:23,180
I want to be in charge
of all international business,

569
00:35:23,287 --> 00:35:24,754
and I have to be president.

570
00:35:24,856 --> 00:35:27,484
Creative reports to me,
or the whole thing falls apart.

571
00:35:34,999 --> 00:35:37,399
Thank you for thinking of us.

572
00:35:39,737 --> 00:35:41,295
To old friends.

573
00:35:46,043 --> 00:35:47,601
Hello.

574
00:35:47,712 --> 00:35:50,272
Did you have any trouble finding me?

575
00:35:50,381 --> 00:35:51,609
Neighbors.

576
00:35:51,716 --> 00:35:52,808
Right.

577
00:35:54,519 --> 00:35:55,884
