My, oh, my. A case.

643
00:41:13,103 --> 00:41:14,900
They're all there. I checked.

644
00:41:15,005 --> 00:41:16,939
All the card says is that it's for you.

645
00:41:18,242 --> 00:41:20,472
Well, thank you, Miss Holloway.

